projects.title: AngularQuiz
details: Engineered a full-stack quiz platform using Angular (frontend) and Flask (backend), supporting real-time scoring, leaderboards, and secure authentication for 50+ concurrent users.
Developed REST APIs in Flask and linked a relational database to manage 1,000+ quiz questions and user scores.
Enabled real-time competition, increasing engagement with live leaderboard updates every second.
Deployed the application locally for testing and demonstration, gaining hands-on experience in clientâ€“server architecture, authentication flows, and state management.
